0.102 0.235 0.431 rg
51.0236220472441033 598.1104724409448181 Td
(Kedua modul berinteraksi secara asinkron melalui antarmuka REST API. Ketika client menekan tombol submit booking,) Tj
T* (Modul Pemesanan mengirimkan payload HTTP POST request ke endpoint backend. Controller backend memanggil Stock) Tj
T* (Collision Guard untuk melakukan validasi relasional silang sebelum merekam data ke database.) Tj
T* (• HTTP Endpoint: POST /api/bookings/validate-and-create) Tj
T* (• Payload Request: { client_id: UUID, event_date: "2026-05-25", items: [{ equipment_id: 102, quantity: 15 }] }) Tj
T* (• HTTP Response Sukses \(200 OK\): { status: "success", booking_id: 4091, message: "Booking allowed" }) Tj
T* (• HTTP Response Konflik \(409 Conflict\): { status: "failed", error: "Stock Collision Error", shortfall: 5 }) Tj
